whole hand in there.

12:46.140 --> 12:48.802
Oh.

12:49.102 --> 12:50.388
Yay.

12:50.687 --> 12:52.428
Hey, where did my strawberry go?

12:52.730 --> 12:54.141
Sweetie,
you don't have to do this.

12:54.440 --> 12:56.602
Where did you go?
You should probably go to bed.

12:56.901 --> 12:59.814
You know, the doctor said
he's surprised you're alive.

13:00.113 --> 13:01.945
Got my third wind. Yeah.

13:02.240 --> 13:05.858
Oh, what time is it?
We gotta go.

13:06.160 --> 13:08.447
Max is gonna pick us up
and take us to Tableau.

13:08.746 --> 13:09.986
In his limo.

13:10.290 --> 13:12.406
[BOTH CHUCKLING]

13:12.709 --> 13:14.495
[SNORES]

13:14.794 --> 13:16.125
Fourth wind!

13:16.421 --> 13:21.006
Valentine's Day
is the best day to do whites.

13:21.301 --> 13:23.793
