you did your laundry,

13:29.684 --> 13:31.641
and spent 45 minutes
photographing your Game Genie

13:31.936 --> 13:33.017
for an eBay auction.

13:33.313 --> 13:35.350
Lindsay, I know
about the breakup window.

13:35.648 --> 13:38.436
What are you talking about?
Oh, come on. "Work was crazy."

13:38.735 --> 13:40.271
Then you said you had to pick up
a present for me.

13:40.570 --> 13:42.231
You said you had a friend
in town.

13:42.530 --> 13:44.646
Nobody ever has a friend
in town.

13:44.949 --> 13:47.407
Work has been crazy,
and I do have a friend in town.

13:47.702 --> 13:49.693
And we were gonna give you
your dream gift.

13:49.996 --> 13:51.737
Oh. A sit-down with Guy Fieri?

13:52.040 --> 13:54.156
No, Dave. A threesome.

13:54.459 --> 13:56.871
[240]

13:57.170 --> 13:58.626
[WHIMPERING]

14:01.007 --> 14:02.497
Oh! Got you!

14:02.800 --> 14:04.006
[LAUGHS]

14:04.302 --> 14:06.168
You guys. I had you going.
| had you going.

14:06.471 --> 14:09.463
| was kidding!
You got faced! You got faced!

14:11.225 --> 14:13.637
